From ad61122b94238883ecb6df19c5eea78e0b74679e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Govindarajulu Varadarajan <govindarajulu.varadarajan@amd.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Oct 2025 17:33:37 -0700
Subject: [LINUX PATCH] xilinx-ai-engine: Protect AXI-MM access during reset of
 partition

When the reset of partition is in progress, this temporarily disables
NSU on a column. Read/Write AXI-MM access during this will cause system
hang. Add rwlock to protect against axi access and reset.

Signed-off-by: Govindarajulu Varadarajan <govindarajulu.varadarajan@amd.com>
(cherry picked from commit 05d12f821cbee0afca3d4c13637e4bfa88230659)
---
 drivers/misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-aie.c | 24 +++----
 .../misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-aie2ps.c  | 44 ++++++-------
 .../misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-aieml.c   | 26 ++++----
 drivers/misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-dma.c | 12 ++--
 .../xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-internal.h     | 49 +++++++++++++-
 .../xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-interrupt.c    | 54 +++++++--------
 .../misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-part.c    | 16 ++---
 drivers/misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-pm.c  | 65 +++++++++++--------
 .../misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-reset.c   | 12 ++--
 .../xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-sysfs-core.c   |  6 +-
 10 files changed, 187 insertions(+), 121 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-aie.c b/drivers/misc/xilinx-ai-engine/ai-engine-aie.c
